---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How DEMWeb Studio collects, stores, and uses information submitted through this site.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-muted">Last updated: 16 July 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-border bg-page px-6 py-5 text-sm text-ink-secondary">
      <strong class="text-ink">Placeholder — legal entity not yet registered.</strong>{' '}
      DEMWeb Studio's business entity is not yet formally registered (expected: Bulgaria). The data controller for
      this site will be listed here as{' '}
      <strong class="text-ink">[Legal entity name and registered address — pending business registration]</strong>{' '}
      once registration is complete.
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-ink-secondary">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink">What we collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          When you submit the contact form on this site, we collect the name, email address, service you're
          interested in, and message you provide. We do not collect any information beyond what you voluntarily
          submit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink">How we use it</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Contact form submissions are used solely to respond to your enquiry. Submissions are delivered by email
          via Resend, a transactional email provider, to the studio's inbox. We do not sell, rent, or share your
          information with third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink">Spam protection</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          The contact form uses Cloudflare Turnstile to prevent spam and abuse. Turnstile runs a challenge in your
          browser and does not use tracking cookies or collect personal data for advertising purposes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink">Analytics</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          This site uses Cloudflare Web Analytics to understand overall traffic and page performance. Cloudflare
          Web Analytics is cookie-free and does not track individual visitors across sites or build a personal
          profile — no cookie consent banner is required or shown on this site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink">Data retention</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Contact form submissions are retained only as long as needed to respond to and resolve your enquiry, or
          as required by law, after which they are deleted.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink">Your rights</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          You can request access to, correction of, or deletion of any information you've submitted by emailing{' '}
          <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`} class="font-medium text-teal hover:underline">{SITE.email}</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Questions about this policy can be sent to{' '}
          <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`} class="font-medium text-teal hover:underline">{SITE.email}</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
